                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The giant crawling hand takes piercing or slashing damage</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> A random creature adjacent to the giant crawling hand is sprayed with vile pus that deals [[/r {4d6}[negative]]]{4d6 negative damage}. The affected creature must attempt a @Check[type:reflex|dc:21|traits:damaging-effect] save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature takes no damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage and becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage and becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 3}.</p>"
